07:24.670 --> 07:27.857
[SPEAKER_00]: service and ridership.

07:28.879 --> 07:41.785
[SPEAKER_00]: That is to go out formulaically 70% of it and then there is a 20% set aside for passenger rail that calls out prioritization for completion of the Northwest Rail and the end line.

07:45.443 --> 07:50.392
[SPEAKER_00]: This is a project overview for the work around joint service.

07:51.013 --> 07:57.545
[SPEAKER_00]: So as I just went through, May 2024, SB 184 and SB 230 was signed into law.

07:58.687 --> 08:03.776
[SPEAKER_00]: In August of 2024, the principles of joint service met.

08:04.016 --> 08:09.426
